===Etymology===
From {{etyl|nl|en}} {{term|kriel|lang=nl||puny/tiny}}, applied to fish [[fry]] (in the sense of hatchlings); sometimes interpreted as "whale food".

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/kɹɪl/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|ɪl|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|krill|krills}}

# any of several small [[marine]] [[crustacean]] [[species]] of [[plankton]] in the [[order]] ''{{taxlink|Euphausiacea|order|noshow=1}}'' in the [[class]] [[Malacostraca]].

